<h1>Fallback Chains (Stable)</h1>
<p>Define ordered list of (model, conditions). When prior fails, next attempted.</p>
<pre><code>policy: {
  fallback: [
    { model: 'gpt-4o' },
    { model: 'claude-3-haiku', on: ['timeout','rate_limit'] },
    { model: 'mistral-medium' }
  ]
}
</code></pre>
<p>Success short-circuits the chain. Combine with race for aggressive latency reduction.</p>
